{
  "stem": "26728.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then if you said, I got one, or whatever, your gun cameras had to prove it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were no unverified kills.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You couldn't say, I got 17 of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There's a-- if your gun camera didn't show that, you didn't get any credit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That's why they had him on there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They had 8 millimeter, then later 16 millimeter cameras on-- two of them-- on-- on fighter planes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] OK that was-- What I was-- what I-- I think I digressed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What I was saying was I really wanted to do more dogfighting because that's what I had been trained to do the most and I thought I was good at.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, there's a certain mentality with fighter pilots.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know whether you've ever gone-- They kind of feel like they're all hot shots, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They wear their clothes differently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- they walk differently.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- they're kind of-- they're not-- there's nothing elite about them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they think there is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They just-- put their pants on the same way as a bomber pilot does.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But-- and the bomber pilots had a great deal more responsibility than the fighter pilots did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The fighter pilots, you just had yourself to worry about and your flight, which was three other airplanes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if you-- if I was assigned to fly a wing on our flight leader, my job was to protect him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had to fly close to him with the two other airplanes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever he did, I had to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If we got jumped, which didn't happen very often, my job was to protect the flight leader's tail.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I had a guy to protect my wing man and which protected my tail, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
